channel.title: Removing doors
channel.description:
Hey guys, I have been 'attempting' to remove a couple of doors. I have put 2 sets of coordinates for the same door under my public void Delete objects, one set of coordinates for each side of the door, just in case. And the door is still there.
So, how do I remove doors???
Any help would be really appreciated, and I don't need to be spoon-fed... all I need to know is what the void to delete doors is, or where I delete them.
Thanks ~ Dai
